WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:04.796
(vocalizing)

00:04.796 --> 00:10.177
♪ ♪

00:10.177 --> 00:12.471
‐New song for Gigi?
‐Nope. You.

00:12.471 --> 00:14.431
I think it's gonna be like
a big, dramatic rocker.

00:14.431 --> 00:15.891
Like a lot of emotional drive.

00:15.891 --> 00:17.518
It could be a great showcase
tune for you.

00:17.518 --> 00:19.186
Oh, cool.
I need one of those.

00:19.186 --> 00:20.729
‐I know.
‐Okay, got my lucky

00:20.729 --> 00:24.358
Micki maracas and where
is my lyrics notebook? Oh.

00:24.358 --> 00:25.859
You know, we, uh,
we could work on

00:25.859 --> 00:27.527
this tune together
right now, honey.

00:27.527 --> 00:29.446
Oh, but I am this close
to finishing

00:29.446 --> 00:32.157
a new tune that Flash and me
came up with.

00:32.157 --> 00:33.534
It's a blues ballad.

00:33.534 --> 00:35.619
He's got a bridge idea
last night

00:35.619 --> 00:37.329
that I am dying to listen to.

00:37.329 --> 00:39.206
Mm‐hmm.
(thunder rumbles)

00:39.206 --> 00:41.416
Oh, awesome.
And he's got a beat

00:41.416 --> 00:44.836
on the second verse.
Okay, I gotta go.

00:44.836 --> 00:46.547
So you have a customized
sound effect

00:46.547 --> 00:48.507
for when Flash texts you,
huh?

00:48.507 --> 00:51.468
Oh, we're going back and forth
with so many ideas these days

00:51.468 --> 00:53.053
that I hear
thunder and lightning

00:53.053 --> 00:54.763
I know it's him
and he needs me to respond.

00:54.763 --> 00:56.139
Right.

00:56.139 --> 00:59.559
(thunder rumbles)

00:59.559 --> 01:01.186
(chuckles)

01:01.186 --> 01:03.355
What‐‐what did he say?

01:03.355 --> 01:06.275
Oh, nothing.
Long story.

01:06.275 --> 01:08.527
Oh, he can be so funny
sometimes.

01:08.527 --> 01:10.028
Yeah.

01:10.028 --> 01:11.071
He's funny.

01:13.448 --> 01:16.660
♪ Sex and drugs
and rock and roll ♪

01:16.660 --> 01:17.744
♪ All right ♪

01:17.744 --> 01:18.870
♪ ♪

